        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:43:32 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:43:32 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Marc Sternfield, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/17/l-a-animal-shelter-hit-with-potentially-deadly-bacterial-outbreak.webp" alt="L.A. animal shelter hit with potentially deadly bacterial outbreak"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">L.A. animal shelter hit with potentially deadly bacterial outbreak</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A Los Angeles animal shelter is diverting pets to other facilities due to an outbreak of a highly contagious and potentially deadly respiratory illness, Streptococcus zooepidemicus, or strep zoo.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/17/l-a-animal-shelter-hit-with-potentially-deadly-bacterial-outbreak/"  >(Marc Sternfield, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 00:31:39 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 00:31:39 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Patrick Djordjevic, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/16/recall-for-candy-sold-at-walmart-target-upgraded-to-highest-risk-level.webp" alt="Recall for candy sold at Walmart, Target upgraded to highest risk level"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Recall for candy sold at Walmart, Target upgraded to highest risk level</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Palmer Candy Company in Sioux City, Iowa recalled "white coated confectionary items" due to the possibility of contamination
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/16/recall-for-candy-sold-at-walmart-target-upgraded-to-highest-risk-level/"  >(Patrick Djordjevic, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 20:16:45 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 20:16:45 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Gabby Allen, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/15/tsa-finds-stun-gun-disguised-as-iphone-at-dc-area-airport.webp" alt="TSA finds stun gun disguised as iPhone at DC-area airport"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">TSA finds stun gun disguised as iPhone at DC-area airport</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      "Right at the bottom where you would normally plug in, it's got little prongs that indicate that that's where you would get zapped," a TSA spokesperson  said of the device.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/15/tsa-finds-stun-gun-disguised-as-iphone-at-dc-area-airport/"  >(Gabby Allen, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:48:50 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 19:48:50 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/17/florida-school-psychologist-charged-with-possessing-and-distributing-child-sexual-abuse-material.webp" alt="Florida school psychologist charged with possessing and distributing child sexual abuse material"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Florida school psychologist charged with possessing and distributing child sexual abuse material</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A South Florida school psychologist has been arrested and charged with possessing and distributing child sexual abuse images and videos, officials said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/17/florida-school-psychologist-charged-with-possessing-and-distributing-child-sexual-abuse-material/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 01:42:24 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 01:42:24 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
