  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/15/astronauts-may-be-stuck-in-space-until-2025-what-it-could-mean-for-their-bodies.webp" alt="Astronauts may be stuck in space until 2025: What it could mean for their bodies"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Astronauts may be stuck in space until 2025: What it could mean for their bodies</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A two week journey to the International Space Station could become an eight month stay for two astronauts.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/15/astronauts-may-be-stuck-in-space-until-2025-what-it-could-mean-for-their-bodies/"  >(Eric Henrikson, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:33:06 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:33:06 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Yash Roy, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/17/harris-trump-polling.webp" alt="Harris, Trump neck and neck in 4 critical swing states: Survey"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris, Trump neck and neck in 4 critical swing states: Survey</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Harris is closing the gap with former President Trump in several key battleground states as the election inches closer
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/17/harris-trump-polling/"  >(Yash Roy, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 22:48:38 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 18 Aug 2024 22:48:38 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
