           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Is the gen AI bubble due to burst? CIOs face rethink ahead</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Generative AI has been hyped so much over the past two years that observers see an inevitable course correction ahead — one that should prompt CIOs to rethink their gen AI strategies.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/15/is-the-gen-ai-bubble-due-to-burst-cios-face-rethink-ahead/"  >(CIO)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2024-08-15T12:43:49">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2024-08-15T12:43:49">
