           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google AI Overviews gets upgrades, expands to these 6 countries</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Google parent Alphabet said on Thursday it was expanding its AI-generated summaries for search queries to six new countries, just two months after it rolled back some capabilities following a problem-riddled launch.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/08/15/google-ai-overviews-gets-upgrades-expands-these-6-countries/"  >(Reuters, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:00:00 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:00:00 +0000">
