    <h3 itemprop="headline">Final Bay Bridge Series kicks off with season-high crowd, &#8216;emotional&#8217; Jose Canseco</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      OAKLAND, Calif. (AP) — The atmosphere felt like old times in Oakland for Mark Kotsay and Bob Melvin. And for Mark Canha and Matt Chapman, a couple of former Athletics stars now wearing the rival's jersey.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/18/final-bay-bridge-series-kicks-off-with-season-high-crowd-emotional-jose-canseco/"  >(JANIE McCAULEY, Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
