           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Brooks Koepka wins LIV Golf Greenbrier in a playoff over Rahm</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WHITE SULPHUR SPRINGS, W.Va. (AP) — Brooks Koepka picked up his second LIV Golf League victory of the year Sunday when he shot 7-under 63 at The Greenbrier and beat Jon Rahm with a par on the first playoff hole.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/19/brooks-koepka-wins-liv-golf-greenbrier-in-a-playoff-over-rahm/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
