           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Yankees and Tigers are kids for a day, mingling among Little Leaguers</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Detroit Tigers and New York Yankees were like kids again as they mingled with Little Leaguers ahead of the Major League Baseball Little League Classic on Sunday night.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/18/yankees-and-tigers-are-kids-for-a-day-mingling-among-little-leaguers/"  >(Dan Gelston, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
