    <h3 itemprop="headline">Kickin' off Tampa Bay Sun FC gameday with pro soccer hopefuls</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Tampa Bay Sun Football Club will kick off its first season Sunday night at Riverfront Stadium in Tampa.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/18/kickin-off-tampa-bay-sun-fc-gameday-with-pro-soccer-hopefuls/"  >(Chloe Sparks, WFLA, NBC)</a>
