           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NASCAR Cup race at Michigan suspended until Monday after rain, rain wouldn't go away</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BROOKLYN, Mich. (AP) — NASCAR suspended the FireKeepers 400 until Monday, running out of time Sunday to run a race that was delayed and interrupted by rain.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/18/nascar-cup-race-at-michigan-suspended-until-monday-after-rain-rain-wouldnt-go-away/"  >(LARRY LAGE, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
