      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/08/18/minnesota-vikings-agree-to-1-year-contract-with-veteran-cornerback-stephon-gilmore.webp" alt="Minnesota Vikings agree to 1-year contract with veteran cornerback Stephon Gilmore"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Minnesota Vikings agree to 1-year contract with veteran cornerback Stephon Gilmore</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Minnesota Vikings agreed to a one-year contract with Stephon Gilmore on Sunday, the fifth cornerback — and by far the most accomplished — the team has added since training camp began in an effort to bolster a vital position group.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/18/minnesota-vikings-agree-to-1-year-contract-with-veteran-cornerback-stephon-gilmore/"  >(DAVE CAMPBELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
