           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Hideki Matsuyama avoids collapse and rallies to win FedEx Cup playoffs opener</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MEMPHIS, Tenn. (AP) — Hideki Matsuyama could feel the tournament getting away from him, an odd sensation considering he had gone 27 holes without a bogey and had a five-shot lead just an hour earlier. Even more improbable was how it ended Sunday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/08/19/hideki-matsuyama-avoids-collapse-and-rallies-to-win-fedex-cup-playoffs-opener/"  >(DOUG FERGUSON, Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
