    <h3 itemprop="headline">How Elon Musk is using his wealth, reach to support Trump's campaign</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      After years of drifting toward the political right, the billionaire owner of Tesla and SpaceX is throwing his fortune behind a pro-Trump super PAC.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/15/elon-musk-wealth-trump-support/"  >(Taylor Giorno, NewsNation)</a>
