           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">GOP leaders push House members to raise more cash to combat Harris enthusiasm</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Richard Hudson (R-N.C.), the chair of the House GOP campaign arm, encouraged members to ramp up fundraising efforts and investment Thursday during a private conference call, as Vice President Harris’s nascent White House bid intensifies Democratic enthusiasm.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/16/gop-leaders-push-house-members-to-raise-more-cash-to-combat-harris-enthusiasm/"  >(Emily Brooks, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
