           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Harris campaign buys ads on Fox News: Report</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The campaign began with four commercials that ran Wednesday, each attempting to contrast Harris with Republican opponent Donald Trump.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/16/harris-campaign-buys-ads-on-fox-news-report/"  >(NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
