    <meta itemprop="name" content="Deepa Shivaram, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/16/how-to-say-kamala-and-why-it-makes-a-difference.webp" alt="How to say &#8216;Kamala&#8217; &#8212; and why it makes a difference"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How to say &#8216;Kamala&#8217; &#8212; and why it makes a difference</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      As Vice President Harris has risen up in the political world, the name “Kamala” is getting more airtime. And on the campaign trail, Harris’ name is often intentionally mispronounced by her opponent.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/16/how-to-say-kamala-and-why-it-makes-a-difference/"  >(Deepa Shivaram, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:08:07 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:08:07 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Amie Parnes, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/16/democrats-warn-against-overconfidence-amid-harris-momentum.webp" alt="Democrats warn against overconfidence amid Harris momentum"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Democrats warn against overconfidence amid Harris momentum</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Democrats know they're winning the presidential race right now. But they also know how quickly that could change.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/16/democrats-warn-against-overconfidence-amid-harris-momentum/"  >(Amie Parnes, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
